quran[9{c,v,t}:
40,41,"ae qoum, aakhir yeh kya maajra hai ke mein to tum logon ko nijaat ki taraf bulaataa hon aur tum log mujhe aag ki taraf dawat dete ho !"
40,42,"tum mujhe is baat ki dawat dete ho ke mein Allah se kufar karoon aur is ke sath unn hstyon ko shareektehraؤں jinhein mein nahi jaanta, halaank mein tumhe uss zabardast mughfirat karne walay khuda ki taraf bulaa raha hon"
40,43,"nahi, haq yeh hai aur iss ke khilaaf nahi ho sakta ke jin ki taraf tum mujhe bulaa rahay ho unn ke liye nah duniya mein koi dawat hai nah akhirat mein, aur hum sab ko palatna Allah hi ki taraf hai, aur hadd se guzarnay walay aag mein jaane walay hain"
40,44,"aaj jo kuch mein keh raha hon, anqareeb woh waqt aeye ga jab tum ussay yaad karo ge aur apna maamla mein Allah ke supurd karta hon, woh apne bundon ka nigehbaan hai """
40,45,"aakhir kaar unn logon ne jo buri se buri chaalein uss momin ke khilaaf chalein, Allah ne unn sab se uss ko bacha liya, aur firaon ke saathi khud bad tareen azaab ke phair mein aa gay"
40,46,"dozakh ki aag hai jis ke samnay subah o shaam woh paish kiye jatay hain, aur jab qayamat ki gharri aa jaye gi to hukum ho ga ke all firaon ko shadeed tar azaab mein daakhil karo"
40,47,"phir zara khayaal karo uss waqt ka jab yeh log dozakh mein aik dosray se jhagar rahay hon ge duniya mein jo log kamzor thay woh barray ban'nay walon se kahin ge ke"" hum tumahray tabay thay, ab kya yahan tum naar jahannum ki takleef ke kuch hissay se hum ko bacha lau ge? """
40,48,"woh barray ban'nay walay jawab den ge"" hum sab yahan aik haal mein hain, aur Allah bundon ke darmain faisla kar chuka hai """
40,49,"phir yeh dozakh mein parre hue log jahannum ke ahal karon se kahin ge"" apne rab se dua karo ke hamaray azaab mein bas aik din ki takhfeef kar day """
